game.name: Anna Wedding Cake And Decor
game.description:
A big wedding occasion is going to be taken place. As you know that frozen Princess Anna was in love with Kristoff, so she has accepted his marriage proposal and got ready to marry him. Now Elsa (Anna sister) wants a beautiful wedding cake for her marriage. In this free online cooking game, your job is to help her in doing so and also decorate the assembly hall to make her feel good. Your help will be a valuable assistance for her while she encountering various problems.?

In this cool cooking game for girls, your cooking and creativity skills are improved dynamically. You will surely enjoy this highly exciting and beautifully-designed game when you help Elsa to make all the arrangements required to make her sister marriage a memorable event for her family. Follow all the useful and helpful instructions and try to make the highly delicious cake for her. Once you are prepared it, do not forget to decorate it with the help of other scrumptious items.?

There will be an awesome and unforgettable wedding event made by Anna and Kristoff. Frozen is looking for your help. Do not wait anymore! Come and take the charge of cooking a delicious wedding cake you have not created before. Anna also carries some unique and fantastic decorating options right from your trendy styles before finalizing which one to select for her big day. Good luck and enjoy!
